1
00:00:00,080 --> 00:00:02,399
At some point in your life, you're

2
00:00:01,199 --> 00:00:03,201
probably going to be asked to give a

3
00:00:02,480 --> 00:00:03,839
presentation. And this can be a great

4
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:08,400
opportunity for you, but only if you

5
00:00:06,318 --> 00:00:10,319
prepare correctly. Otherwise, it's an

6
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:11,920
opportunity for failure. Even if you are

7
00:00:10,320 --> 00:00:13,598
a great speaker, even if you're

8
00:00:11,919 --> 00:00:15,278
charismatic and confident and you're

