15
00:00:25,278 --> 00:00:28,639
way. Fortunately, communicating your

16
00:00:27,118 --> 00:00:30,638
ideas to an audience in a way that's

17
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:32,718
persuasive and exciting is a skill that

18
00:00:30,640 --> 00:00:34,479
you can learn and get better at. So,

19
00:00:32,719 --> 00:00:36,078
today I want to share four big ideas

20
00:00:34,479 --> 00:00:38,159
that you can use to start crafting and

21
00:00:36,079 --> 00:00:39,599
delivering better presentations. And

22
00:00:38,159 --> 00:00:41,759
speaking of skills that you can learn,

